---
const {percentage, topics=["AutoComplete"]} = Astro.props
---

<div class="bg-red-400 px-5 py-1 font-sans border-black border-2">
    <h3>
        This article was >={percentage}% written using AI.
    </h3>
    <p class="p-0 leading-relaxed">
        The above article was written with the help of AI in the form of 
        GitHub Copilot and GPT-3. The AI was used to generate the following
    </p>
    <ul>
        {
            //@ts-ignore
            topics.map(topic => {
                return <li class="font-sans leading-relaxed">{topic}</li>
            })
        }
    </ul>
    <p class="leading-relaxed">
        Content generated by AI can sometimes be inaccurate or misleading.
        Please use your own judgement when reading this article.
        Moreover, the AI is not perfect and may have made mistakes.
        I am sorry for the mistakes, but I am not responsible for them.
    </p>
</div>